            .content-visitorID.col-7
                h4 What is Visitor ID?
                p Visitor ID with Browsify is a unique string of characters assigned to each user based on their device, no matter which browser they use. Even if they reinstall their OS or switch browsers, Browsify consistently detects the same Visitor ID.
        .visitorID-work.containerr
            .content-vtID-work.col-5
                h4 How Does Visitor ID Work?
                .list-answer.mt-3.d-flex.align-items-center
                    img.me-2(src="/img/ic-vt.svg", alt="")
                    span Assigns a unique ID to every device user.
                .list-answer.mt-3.d-flex.align-items-center
                    img.me-2(src="/img/ic-global.svg", alt="")
                    span Stays the same across browsers (e.g., Chrome, Firefox).
                .list-answer.mt-3.d-flex.align-items-center
                    img.me-2(src="/img/ic-change.svg", alt="")
                    span Persists through OS reinstalls or settings changes.
                .list-answer.mt-3.d-flex.align-items-center
                    img.me-2(src="/img/ic-secur.svg", alt="")
                    span Tracks users securely without relying on cookies or IPs.
            .col-7
